    "description": "<i>Star Shift Origins</i> 讲述了“Dauntless”号舰船的首批船员的故事。他们被困在了一个替代现实中，并在逃亡中。在被无情的地球系统联盟 (ESA) 追捕时，船员们拼命寻找答案。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706310/extras/6c21b6278e334c2216caf3f3a1ae0d72.webp?t=1758371193\" width=256 height=50 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706310/extras/223e4989b487d3e9166ac5cf223ddeba.webp?t=1758371193\" width=525 height=30 /></span><br><i>Star Shift Origins</i>中没有等级；技能和属性提升是通过从战斗中获得的知识点来管理的。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706310/extras/072aa2c4e35123d991baa16b3c6e77d5.webp?t=1758371193\" width=512 height=30 /></span><br>除了标准的回合制战斗外，还有一个用于舰队和陆军战斗的战术战斗系统。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706310/extras/96670ac18ecb3f44442e78497fac43b3.webp?t=1758371193\" width=512 height=30 /></span><br>根据角色的种族和职业，存在独特的技能树。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706310/extras/18944390806a0da00b22706bc401d6b6.webp?t=1758371193\" width=512 height=30 /></span><br>时间已经破碎。只有你和你的船员才能在太迟之前解开这个谜团！<br><br><br><br>由多位独立艺术家创作的音乐原声带，增强了游戏体验。<br>",
